snippet.title: The Curse of Illmoore Bay Demo Playthrough
snippet.description:
A playthrough of the demo of The Curse of Illmoore Bay by artist Jav!

The Curse of Illmoore Bay is a platforming adventure for the Sega Genesis/Mega Drive, due out in June 2020!
Download the latest demo or pre-order your copy at: http://www.second-dimension.com/shop/product/33
